执行以下代码，输出什么？
```cpp
int a[5] = {2, 4, 6, 8, 10};
int sum = 0;
for (int i = 1; i < 4; i++)
    sum += a[i];
cout << sum;
```

执行以下代码，输出什么？
```cpp
string s = "dynamic";
